contentrichtext.text: '''Qeqertarsuatsiaq''' may refer to several locations in West [[Greenland]]: * [[Qeqertarsuatsiaq Island]] (also known as ''Hareø'') to the northwest of [[Disko Island]], Greenland * A steep cliff on [[Qeqertarsuatsiaq Island]] (Hareø), Greenland at {{coord|70|23|N|54|49|W}}<ref>[http://www.dmu.dk/NR/rdonlyres/3B15B076-73D3-4227-800A-78DE7CEBD091/0/Sites2006.xls DMU - 404]</ref> * An abandoned settlement in Greenland located at approximately {{coord|68|09|N|53|06|W}}<ref>[http://www.arktiskebilleder.dk/siulleq/album/sted_7001989_1.html Siulleq Qeqertarsuatsiaq<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref> * A location near [[Qeqertarsuatsiaat]] ({{lang-da|Fiskenæsset}}), Greenland at approximately {{coord|63|08|N|50|40|W}}<ref>http://www.geus.dk/departments/quaternary-marine-geol/oliespild_v_gr/PDFfiles/Chapter9/Map6302L.pdf</ref> == References == {{reflist}} {{disambig}}
